beer.beer_name: Don't Judge A Beer By It's Colour
beer.beer_description: Vanilla, Single Origin Campos Coffee & Cacao nibs recreate the dark malt characters of stout in this challenge of the senses. Looks can be deceiving, so shut your eyes to explore flavour & aroma. then open them for a surprise of colour. Enjoy!
